An Act relative to waste disposal.
Be it enacted by the Senate and House of Representatives in General Court assembled, and by the authority
of the same, as follows:
1 Section 16 of Chapter 270 of the General Laws, as appearing in the 2022 Official Edition,
2 is hereby amended by inserting at the end thereof, the following words:-
3 Large waste disposal bags that are at or are exceeding the dimensions of: eight feet in
4 width, two and one-half feet in height, and 4 feet in depth, shall have affixed on its strap handles
5 and siding an identifying serial number. Sellers of such disposal bags shall have a tracking
6 system in place using said serial numbers to ensure proper disposal of waste.
